{"tid":1517484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之後再無遊行或集會","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:27:51.000Z","uid":313312,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"73a483165ea8f2e8cb6397dc60fe343391cd99cc","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"只有戰場，如果上得戰場請有殺敵心態，對家已經唔會當你係人看待，仲抱有道德去抗爭，只會傷害自己。全面解開技能，火魔法，流星雨，唔好再猶豫用唔用。唔好天真再好似64既年青人一樣，記住自己生命係自己負責，戰場上對敵人仁慈，就對自己殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n另外戰術上可以提供意見<br />\n<br />\n中排唔敢上前可以投擲支援<br />\n除左x頭，仲有大家成日講蛋，我有野更好推薦-黃膠水，好處本身有一定硬度，會有扣hp同時可以減速，乾左仲會限制活動能力，帶有傳染性，而且清潔會有一定難定，可能要報廢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2k7HdK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2k7HdK.jpg&h=d6267f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47HqtTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47HqtTL.jpg&h=3a233a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路障小隊<br />\n請在前線前方設置魚絲，魚絲好處拉力強，有纏繞性，而且巨透明性難以發覺，就算班狗知有魚絲都要慢慢搵出黎，俾更多前線撤退或反擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94v3Z4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94v3Z4h.jpg&h=33e4bdcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申講war game"},{"pid":"ffffd4a510e3a4deda60fa69f1478dfb28ba9992","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1b7b0ef6a7168024d1421850256b643a5be4d092","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"af26b97b028a389a19fda3eb8682b67331dc4d8a","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"104eb430adcf0631577f08d0e173236794f028e9","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"74d085e1c767858079454495e87e199ca3205aee","tid":1517484,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco